a) set up NLP model for processing expressions into positional arguments of political nature
b) make a website where people can
	1) answer political questions about topics
	2) suggest new political topics and questions
	3) ask model for information about collected opinions
c) give model A 
	1) ability to write datapoints of collected opinionated data keyed to account into database
	2) capability to improve questions depending on answers previously given -> feedback loop on clarity and brevity of answers
d) give model B 
	1) capability to answer demographic questions about preferences of demographic, including statistics and qualitative analysis

end result:
highly scalable democracy with statistical accountability without need of human knowledge of the political opinion of others. (world at [military] peace.)
